{
  "stem": "19550.9",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "The-- the world was not very welcoming to the survivors.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Clearly, even someone like me, who had, as I say, this anchor in-- in America, could not find a way to get to America.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Nobody was eager to have us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] In-- in-- in fact, you know, the truth of the matter is that nobody really liberated us.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Nobody fought to liberate us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "We were in-- on the way, as people or as army units passed by a concentration camp, they liberated it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "But nobody really made any sacrifice or any direct move to-- to liberate concentration camp prisoners.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And similarly, after our liberation, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] in a-- in a measure, of course, nobody was prepared with what they were going-- for what they were going to find and didn't know how to deal with them-- with it.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And there were, of course, Jew-- Jewish organizations and UNRRA and-- and the Jewish agency that were groping towards ways of trying to-- to help.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "But, you know, the political considerations and complications didn't really permit-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] certainly not for compensation for the suffering of these people, by the way they were being received after their survival.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "I'm not speaking of individual efforts that were made by various people, like the chaplains in the-- in the American army or some military governors who had a deeper understanding or a-- or a more human sympathy.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "But by and large, the world was closed to us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Those who wanted to go to Palestine-- of course Palestine was closed.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Those who wanted to go to North America, it-- it wasn't only that there were no civilian authorities to whom you could apply for a visa.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
